import React from 'react'
import { Menu, Icon } from 'antd'
import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom"

const PageMenu = () =>
    <Menu mode="horizontal" theme="dark" selectable={false}>
        <Menu.Item key="home">
            <NavLink to="/">
                <Icon type="home" /> Home
            </NavLink>
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item key="films">
            <NavLink to="/films">
                <Icon type="smile" /> Films
            </NavLink>
        </Menu.Item>
    </Menu>

export default PageMenu
